ull, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012493, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, indeed I ask you, O One Who is what He is. And there is nothing like Him except Himself. O One Who does not know what He is except that He is. O One Whom nothing can make helpless, and nothing is a replacement for Him, and He is the Creator of everything, and the One Who controls everything, and One in Whose control is everything, the dominant One over everything, Who destroyed the tyrants by His power.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA YAA MAN HOWA HOWA. WA LAYSA SHAI-UN KAHOWA ILLAA HOWA. YAA MAL LAA HOWA YA’LAMU MAA HOWA ILLAA HUW. YAA MAN LAA YA’JEZOHU SHAI-UN. WA YA’TAAZO A’LAYHI SHAYIN. WA KHAALEQO KULLE SHAYIN. WA MODABBERO KULLE SHAY. WA MAN FEE QABZATEHI KULLA SHAYIN. QAAHERO LEKULLE SHAYIN. QAMA-A’L JABAABERATE BEBA-SEHI. WA ASTA’BADAL KHALQA BE-SULTAANEH. ANTAL LAZEE KHASHA-A’T LAKA KULLO NAASIYYAH.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْاَلُكَ يَا مَنْ هُوَ هُوَ، وَلَيْسَ شَیْءٌ كَهُوَ اِلَّا هُوَ، يَا مَنْ لَا يَعْلَمُ مَا هُوَ اِلَّا هُوَ، يَا مَنْ لَا يَعْجِزُهٗ شَیْءٌ، وَلَا يَعْتَاضُ عَلَيْهِ شَیْءٍ، وَخَالِقُ كُلِّ شَیْءٍ، وَمُدَبِّرُ كُلِّ شَیْءٍ، وَمَنْ فِيْ قَبْضَتِهٖ كُلُّ شَیْءٍ، قَاهِرٌ لِكُلِّ شَیْءٍ، قَمَعَ الْجَبَابِرَةِ بِبَاسِهٖ، وَاسْتَعْبَدَ الْخَلْقَ بِسُلْطَانِهٖ، اَنْتَ الَّذِیْ خَشَعَتْ لَكَ كُلُّ نَاصِيَّةٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012495, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "One Who demands worship of the creatures by His power. O You are the One for whom every forehead bows. And all the beings submit to Your lordship, the closest and the distant ones, You know the apparent and the hidden and what is there from everything more hidden. O One Who knows the blinks of the eyes and what the hearts conceal in the depths of the secrets. O One Who knows what was and what will be. O One in Whose control is the kingdom of the heavens and the earth. O One Who is the Creator of the heavens and the earth.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA AD-A’NAT BE-ROBOOBIYYATEKA KULLO NAFSIN DAANEYATIN WA QAASIYYA TA’LAMUS SIRRA WANNAJWAA, WA MAA HOWA MIN KULLE SHAY-IN AKHFAA. YAA MAYN YA’LAMO LAHAZAATIL JOFOONE, WA MAA TUKHFEEHIL QOLOOBO MIN GHAAMEZIL MAKNOON, YAA MAN YA’LAMO MAA KAANA WA MAA YAKOON, YAA MAM BE-YADEHI MALAKOOTUS SAMAAWAATE WAL ARZ, YAA BADEEA’S SAMAAWAATE WAL ARZ.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَذْعَنَتْ بِرُبُوْبِيَّتِكَ كُلُّ نَفْسٍ دَانِيَةٍ وَقَاصِيَّةٍ، تَعْلَمُ السِّرَّ وَالنَّجْوٰی، وَمَا هُوَ مِنْ كُلِّ شَیْءٍ اَخْفٰی، يَا مَنْ يَعْلَمُ لَحَظَاتِ الْجُفُوْنِ، وَمَا تُخْفِيْهِ الْقُلُوْبُ مِنْ غَامِضِ الْمَكْنُوْنِ، يَا مَنْ يَعْلَمُ مَا كَانَ وَمَا يَكُوْنُ، يَا مَنْ بِيَدِةِ مَلَكُوْتُ السَّمٰوَاتُ وَاْلَارْضُ، يَا بَدِيْعَ السَّمٰوَاتِ وَاْلَارْضِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012497, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O One in Whose control is the kingdom of everything. And He is such that nothing could oppress Him. Save us by Your kindness from whatever we fear. And convey to us what we hope for. O One on Whom is not hidden the most subtle and the most hidden and the most revered of the revered. O master! The hopes are cut off except from You, and the hopes are not reposed except in You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "YAA MAN BE-YADEHI MALAKOOTO KULLE SHAY. WA HOWA LAA YOJAARO A’LAYH. AJIRNAA BE-LUTFEKA MIMMAA NATTAQEE. WA BALLIGHNA BE-QUDRATEKA MAA NARTAJEE. YAA MAN LAA YUKHFAA A’LAYHID DAQEEQUL KHAFEE. WA LAL JALEELUL JALEE. YAA MAWLAAYAN QATA-A’R RAJAA-O ILLAA MIN-KA, WA KHAABATIL AAMAALO ILLAA FEEK.", "ArabicText1": "يَا مَنْ بِيَدِهٖ مَلَكُوْتُ۔ كُلِّ شَىْءٍ، وَهُوَ لَا يُجَارُ عَلَيْهِ، اَجِرْنَا بِلُطْفِكَ مِمَّا نَتَقِّيْ، وَ