l, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012499, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I ask you for the sake of those whose right is obligatory upon You. Whose rights You have appointed worthy near You. That You bless Muhammad and the Progeny of Muhammad and that You fulfill my need, and that You convey me to my safety, and fulfill my hopes, then I indeed ask You and I know that You are the great Lord, One Whom nothing can make helpless when You have intended it.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "AS-ALOKA BE-HAQQE MIN HAQQEHI WAAJEBUN A’LAIK. MIMMAN JA-A’LTA LAHOMUL HAQQA I’NDAK. AN TOSALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMAD. WA AN TAQZEYA HAAJATEE. WA AN TOBALLEGHANEE AMNEYATEE. WA TUNJEZA LEE AMALEE. FAINNEE AS-ALOKA WA AA’LAMO INNAKAR RABBUL A’ZEEM. ALLAZEE LAA YO’JEZOKA SHAI-UN EZAA ARADTOH.", "ArabicText1": "اَسْاَلُكَ بِحَقِّ مِنْ حَقِّهٖ وَاجِبٌ عَلَيْكَ، مِمَّنْ جَعَلْتَ لَهُمُ الْحَقِّ عِنْدَكَ، اَنْ تُصَلِّىَ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَاَنْ تَقْضِىَ حَاجَتِىْ، وَاَنْ تُبَلِّغَنِيْ اَمْنِيَتِىْ، وَتُنْجِزَ لِىْ اَمَلِىْ، فَاِنِّيْ اَسْاَلُكَ وَاَعْلَمُ اَنَّكَ الرَّبُّ الْعَظِيْمُ، الَّذِىْ لَا يُعْجِزُكَ شَىْءٌ اِذَا اَرَدْتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012501, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, indeed I pass the day and night in Your kingdom and Your protection, then give me recompense. O Allah, and my family and my children, whom You have created and what You created. O the great One. And We have made before them a barrier and a barrier behind them, then We have covered them over so that they do not see. In the name of Allah, the Beneficent the Merciful, There is no god except Allah, He is the living, the eternal.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE ASBEHO WA AMSEE FEE ZEMAAMEKA WA JEWAAREK. FA AJIRNEE ALLAAHUMMA WA AHLEE WA WULDEE MIMMAN KHALAQTA WA MAA KHALAQTA. YAA AZEEMO INNAA JA-A’LNAA MIM BAYNE AYDEEHIM SADDAN WA MIN KHALFEHIM SADDAN FA-AGHSHAYNAAHUM FAHUM LAA YUBSEROON. BISMIL LAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM. ALLAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA HOWAL HAYYUL QAYYOOM.", "ArabicText1": "اَللَّهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَصْبِحَ وَاَمْسِىْ فِيْ ذِمَامِكَ وَجِوَارِكَ، فاَجِرْنِيْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ وَاَهْلِيْ وَ وُلْدِىْ مِمَّنْ خَلَقْتَ وَمَا خَلَقْتَ، يَا عَظِيْمُ (اِنَّا جَعَلْنَا مِنْ بَيْنِ اَيْدِيْهِمْ سَدًّا وَّمِنْ خَلْفِهِمْ سَدًّا فَاَغْشَيْنَاهُمْ فَهُمْ لَا يُبْصِرُوْنَ) بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْمِ، اَللهِ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا هُوَ الْحَىُّ الْقَيُّوْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012503, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah then by them and by Your names greater than them. Place us in the refuge and shield from everything we dread, and from the mischief of the ruler and the mischief of the Satan and the mischief of all the beasts and quadrupeds and crawling creatures and the darknesses of the night and the coming out of the day, and from all the concealed matters that I fear.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA FABEHEMA WA BISMEKAL AA’ZAME MINHOMAA. IJ-A’LNAA FEE HIRZIN WA JUNNATIN MIN KULLE MAA NATTAQEEHE. WA MIN SHARRIS SULTAAN. WA MIN SHARRISH SHAYTAAN. WA SHARRE KULLE WAHSHIN WA DABEEBIN WA HAWAAMIN WA TAWAAREKIL LAYLE WA KHAWAAREJIN NAHAAR. WA MIN KULLE AMRIM MAKHOOFIN LAA AA’LAMOHU FA-ATTAQEYAH. WA LAA AAMANO AN YAHULLA BEE FA-AHTAWEYAH.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فَبِهِمَا وَبِسْمِكَ الْاَعْظَمِ مِنْهُمَا، اِجْعَلْنَا فِيْ حِرْزٍ وَجَنَّةٍ مِّنْ كُلِّ مَا نَتَّقِيْهِ، وَمِنْ شَرِّ السُّلْطَانِ، وَمِنْ شَرِّ الشَّيْطَانِ، وَشَرِّ كُلِّ وَحْشٍ وَدَبِيْبٍ وَهَوَامٍ وَطوَارِقِ اللَّيْلِ وَخَوَارِجِ النَّهَارِ، وَمِنْ كُلِّ اَمْرٍ مَخُوْفٍ لَا اَعْلَمُهٗ فَاَتَّقِيْهِ، وَلَا آمَنَ اَنْ يَحِلَّ بِىْ فَاَحْتَوِيْهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012505, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "And my courage is in Your hope and all my reliance is on Your reward, then do not deprive me of what I hope for. By there is no god except You, O there is no god except You, by there is no god except You. Save me from all that I fear and fulfill all my needs. And convey to me by Your power what I hope. And one who has oppressed me or whom I fear from the ruler or Satan or all the men, then is appointed there is no god except You on his heart.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA A’QEEDATEE TAWHEEDOKA WA HIMMATEE TAA-MEELOKA WA MOA’WWALEE A’LAA IN-A’A’MEKA FALAA TAHRIMNEE MAA ARTAJEEHE BELAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANT. YAA LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANT. BELAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA IKFENEE MAKHAAWEFEE WA ANILNI MATAALEBEE WA MAN ZALAMANEE AW KHIFTOHU MIN SULTAANIN AW SHAITAANIN AW KULLE INSAAN. FAQAD JA-A’LTO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA A’LAA QALBEHI.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّ عَقِيْدَتِ